            <strong>Power BI is a Business Intelligence platform developed by Microsoft</strong> that allows you to connect multiple data sources, transform them, and create interactive visualizations for business decision-making.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unlike static Excel reports, Power BI offers:
          </p>

