            <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Share dashboards with teams securely</li>
            <li><strong>Microsoft ecosystem integration:</strong> Excel, Teams, SharePoint, Azure</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="not-prose bg-lum-cream rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
