          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-semibold text-lum-black mb-6">Use Cases by Industry</h2>

          <h3>Retail and Commerce</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Sales dashboard:</strong> Sales by store, category, salesperson with drill-down to transaction level</li>
            <li><strong>Inventory analysis:</strong> Turnover, stockouts, days of inventory by SKU</li>
            <li><strong>Competitive analysis:</strong> Price comparison integrated with web scraping</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Professional Services</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Resource utilization:</strong> Billable vs. available hours by consultant</li>
            <li><strong>Project pipeline:</strong> Proposal status, probability of closure</li>
            <li><strong>Client profitability:</strong> Real margin considering hours invested</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Healthcare (Clinics, Medical Centers)</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Scheduling and occupancy:</strong> Occupancy rate by professional and specialty</li>
            <li><strong>No-shows:</strong> Analysis of patients who don't attend and patterns</li>
            <li><strong>Financial indicators:</strong> Billing by insurance type, payment methods</li>
